# OBJECT::FIX_OBJECT_FRAGMENT

## Summary
Resets and brings back all the children. That will leave broken off parts in the world

## Parameters
* **OBJECT_INDEX** object

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Resets an object (has to be a fragment)
